name: "Piss Off" E-girl Poem by Sunny Crittenden
description:
Written in 1998, this emo poem was featured on Sunny's original Angelfire site, along with many other emo poems: https://www.angelfire.com/sd/lilsunny/Poetry.html

I was going through a bad breakup at the time and this was one of the poems I wrote as a result of him seeing someone new he'd assured me when we were together he had no interest in, but was pining for the whole time. Then we broke up, and he used and hurt her too.
